        "Hope this letter finds you in good health and high spirits. I am excited to tell you about my movement from Ontario to Calgary.",
        "You will be elated to know that few days back  I got promoted from Software engineer to the Manager. Due to the requirement of manager in the company\u2019s branch office located in Calgary, the management decided to move me to this location permanently.",
